metadata.name: Faustyna V-001
metadata.description:
Faustyna V-001 - I am sad I don't feel emotions like Humans (still)

Playing on the paradox of our time, this artwork explores our deepest humanity by asking deep questions on what it is to be Human.

A visual draft of the coming multisensory collection 2023, in which each artwork comes with a crafted scent and sound composition.
